{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"KAIXUAN1","fadeType":2,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"sequence":[["The Melancholy of a Princess Chevalier\n\n<size=45>Chapter 1 - Teatime Visitor<\/size>",1]],"stopbgm":true},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"bgm":"story-1","say":"One afternoon at the port...","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"bgmDelay":2,"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Master, Lady Triomphant, please enjoy.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202120},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Le Triomphant and I showed up to join the Royal Navy's tea time.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"I'm honored to have been invited to your famous afternoon tea time.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":801010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"As she spoke, Le Triomphant took out a cutely-wrapped present.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Hmm... So you're the new arrival from Iris Libre?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Good, I see that Iris Libre also cultivates some fine young ladies.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"And you, the commoner over there! You should be more thankful, since I went out of my way to invite you!","options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Thank you very much! Long live the Queen!"}],"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"It seems that Le Triomphant had made a good impression upon Her Majesty.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"If you wanted to look at it a certain way, they certainly seemed to give off the same vibe.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Commander, you were thinking of something rude just now, weren't you?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":801010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"The chief maid, Belfast, was pouring tea for everyone.","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"This aroma is... Darjeeling?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":801010},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Yes. This particular batch was freshly picked in the spring. It's Her Majesty's favorite.","paintingFadeOut":{"time":0.5,"side":1},"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202120},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"I see, so that's why it's so refreshing. I've always heard that the First Flush of Darjeeling is one of the most precious teas.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":801010},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Heh heh, precisely! I can see that you have discerning tastes~â™ª","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_school","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"